                <h1>Unveiling Greek Mythology: Legends & Lore</h1>
                <p>Greek mythology is a rich tapestry of tales about gods, goddesses, heroes, and monsters that shaped ancient Greek culture. Central figures include Zeus, the king of gods, and heroes like Hercules and Achilles, who undertook legendary quests. These myths explore themes of love, power, fate, and humanity's place in the universe.</p>
